<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - Wearable Device</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        header {
            background-color: #333;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }
        header nav a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-left: 20px;
        }
        header nav a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .hero {
            background: url('https://thumbs.dreamstime.com/z/blind-person-walking-stick-street-using-red-white-130545959.jpg') no-repeat center center/cover;
            
            height: 70vh;
            color: white;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 6px;
        }
        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .mission-vision {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            padding: 50px 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .mission, .vision {
            width: 45%;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .mission h2, .vision h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .mission p, .vision p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #555;
        }
        .story-section {
            padding: 50px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .story-section h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .story-section p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #555;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .team-section {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            align-items: center;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 20px 0;
          
        }
        .team-section h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .team-member {
            
            margin: 0 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .team-member img {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .team-member h3 {
            margin-top: 15px;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }
        .team-member p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #555;
        }
        .impact-section {
            padding: 50px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .impact-section h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .impact-stats {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .stat {
            text-align: center;
        }
        .stat h3 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #f04e23;
        }
        .stat p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #555;
        }
        .cta-section {
            background-color: #f04e23;
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .cta-section h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .cta-section a {
            background-color: white;
            color: #f04e23;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        footer {
            background-color: #222;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        footer a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <% layout("/layouts/boilerplate") %>

    <section class="hero">
        <h1>Our Story</h1>
        <p>Empowering the visually impaired to navigate with confidence.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="mission-vision">
        <div class="mission">
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>To improve the lives of visually impaired individuals by providing them with an innovative wearable device that makes navigation simple, safe, and reliable.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="vision">
            <h2>Our Vision</h2>
            <p>We aspire to create a world where technology bridges the gap in accessibility, offering independence and confidence to all individuals with visual impairments.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="story-section">
        <h2>Our Journey</h2>
        <p>Wearable Nav started with a simple idea â€“ to make the world more accessible for visually impaired individuals. After years of research, prototyping, and testing, we developed a state-of-the-art wearable device that uses advanced technology to offer real-time guidance, obstacle detection, and haptic feedback. Our mission is to ensure that no one feels lost or dependent when navigating busy urban environments.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="team-section">
